&lt;h1 id="how-to-do-what-you-love"&gt;How to Do What You Love&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;January 2006&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To do something well you have to like it. That idea is not exactly novel. We&amp;rsquo;ve got it down to four words: &amp;ldquo;Do what you love.&amp;rdquo; But it&amp;rsquo;s not enough just to tell people that. Doing what you love is complicated.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>What Doesn't Seem Like Work?</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/work/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/work/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/work/"&gt;中文版&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
