&lt;h1 id="when-to-do-what-you-love"&gt;When To Do What You Love&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;September 2024&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s some debate about whether it&amp;rsquo;s a good idea to &amp;ldquo;follow your passion.&amp;rdquo; In fact the question is impossible to answer with a simple yes or no. Sometimes you should and sometimes you shouldn&amp;rsquo;t, but the border between should and shouldn&amp;rsquo;t is very complicated. The only way to give a general answer is to trace it.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>